Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 邁步出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚是閃閃發光的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化為甘霖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的東西就捨去 這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在無限廣闊的心中蔓延開來喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於受傷時刻之外　看不見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若現在開始映入雙眸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得強大 抓住機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 無論何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要堅信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想絕對能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遙遠 都不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感覺到明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.50,0:01:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧,武一郎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.09,0:01:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多壞達大人對你所幹的事非常憤怒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎樣負起這個責任?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.55,0:01:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多支達路將軍竟有怪罪他人的資格呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是自己的錯你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為你多餘的插手才令翔龍子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.99,0:02:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,虎王成為了渡的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.93,0:02:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥最重要是講求紀委的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,個人的任意行為我武一郎是不會饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.01,0:02:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四十話\N恐怖的憤怒力量!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.52,0:02:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人面巖啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看,那個很像火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超美人呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,我發現好東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人對著笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔,你好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.30,0:03:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊?虎王!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要背!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王,放我下來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊?虎王!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你精神點了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.49,0:03:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼悲傷的面孔不襯你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,我想也想不到會再見到虎王呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你見到我高興嗎?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和渡果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.91,0:04:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好-朋-友!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.59,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來玩兵捉賊啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來場很沒幹的賽跑決勝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不跟你們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然火美子是第一名呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是終點了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會輸的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也讓我加入吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我弄倒不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我使出東哥羅傳受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必殺,懲罰特別版吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵!混蛋們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適可而止啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的生氣了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!餵,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.34,0:06:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手…請…請停手啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.18,0:06:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不知道你是救世主渡大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還做出了那種事,真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.11,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這拿迪加村是絕對不能憤怒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那樣對待還要我不生氣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要生氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村長先生,為什麼不可以生氣的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個布斯卡布像便是原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.21,0:07:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本那個是叫貓貓倫像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.87,0:07:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是傳播快樂的神像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.70,0:07:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個像看見憤怒的話便會發生大爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.37,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條村便會被炸得七零八落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此便阻止我們生氣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.67,0:07:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為支配這第六星界的黑暗魔術士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.21,0:07:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遙控佔領了神聖的大地亞索加的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遙控?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.49,0:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪惡的黑暗火炎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的仇敵渡的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我死亡遙控吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡他們在拿迪加村嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.24,0:08:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裏應是有布斯加布像在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.04,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星界山第一占蔔師圖星婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問有沒有人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在找星界山第一占蔔師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圖星婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.22,0:08:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說中了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會知…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.49,0:08:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的占蔔從沒錯過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼,難道你便是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.96,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.43,0:09:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是星界山第一大占蔔師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圖星婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆?可是,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我這樣卻已有三千歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個大婆婆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"是嗎?"是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你正在尋找的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.29,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會因巨大的邪惡力量而甦醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.68,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的邪惡力量?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.08,0:09:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那力量不但是救世主渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.35,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連魔界之王多壞達也可比美的絕大力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多…多壞達?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家夥現在在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你,圖星小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大地之父啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請我的力量賜予你生命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.78,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我的魔力變成的魔少女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,到渡他們那裏!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是,死亡遙控大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子那家夥去哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,老虎仔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然找不到火子,但這女孩在哭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.10,0:11:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽媽重要的遺物手鐲被搶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個紅色頭髮的男孩搶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.41,0:11:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手持著魚叉很粗魯的又可怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼不就是海火子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.59,0:11:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我收聲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這家夥是那個叫死亡遙控的家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法造出來的土公仔啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.09,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是他把我重要的手鐲搶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不要被騙了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個了,那是我媽媽的遺物!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火子,你掉了東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是這女孩的手鐲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要還給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎?那我還給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蠢材…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.14,0:12:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是真正的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蠢材啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了,不可以生氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布斯加布像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.65,0:13:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說不可以生氣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以不生氣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要啊海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很糟了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.45,0:13:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我來搔你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收聲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.89,0:13:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…你們會明白我的心情嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.26,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是什麼人在幹擾我的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳,不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷龍劍在發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持有絕大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人的聲音是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在占蔔我們的秘密嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你們這樣做的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個星界的波士死亡遙控啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.07,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好好看清楚!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說得沒錯了吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不對,海火子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.98,0:15:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,我不信你說的話是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不相信同伴是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.14,0:15:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在向海火子道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼叫做道歉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.96,0:15:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得真是對不起別人時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子低下頭,希望對方原諒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.22,0:15:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.01,0:15:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣低下頭,說對不起啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我也要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.12,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.25,0:15:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.84,0:16:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你們一起的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.82,0:16:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪得…看不過眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢複原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.36,0:16:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.17,0:16:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒文)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟可看穿我的魔少女是假的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍星丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了呢,龍星丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧,死與死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.11,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為它是用泥土造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可以自由變形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超飛龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.84,0:17:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.40,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死與死是我用魔力造的魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個程度的攻擊是打不倒它的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又再變形了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.61,0:18:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.11,0:18:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘗嘗這個吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.56,0:18:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣打也打不完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要怎樣做才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那水晶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水晶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王,海火子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那家夥打散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞄準裏面的水晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要失手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.80,0:19:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.31,0:19:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.11,0:19:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.35,0:19:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變形,飛龍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變身,老虎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼豪拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛虎劍攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛龍光擊拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我記著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.72,0:21:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.83,0:21:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有和多壞達比美的力量的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這件事我怎樣也想不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.82,0:21:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.21,0:21:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定會在神聖的亞索加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.10,0:21:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打敗死亡遙控的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.73,0:21:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼,出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.76,0:21:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.88,0:21:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們比賽誰在到達亞索加前道歉得最多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.24,0:21:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.09,0:21:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.59,0:21:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.56,0:21:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.04,0:21:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.99,0:21:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.49,0:21:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是服了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.95,0:22:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.09,0:22:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 陰霾的天空裏烏雲漸漸散去 陽光透過雲層照了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.71,0:22:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人仰望這天空的哪個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眩目的彩虹 即將出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注定出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.06,0:23:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著光線還沒有消失的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.39,0:23:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待著明天的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.64,0:23:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.26,0:23:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生輝的彩虹彼岸裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.63,0:23:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹出了兩個人未來的風
